Create engaging and catchy social media content for a hair care product called Doka Shampoo and Conditioner. The target audience is young women who care about healthy, shiny, and strong hair.
Include:
A short, attention-grabbing hook (first line)
Benefits like smoothness, shine, and hair repair
A fun and trendy tone (Gen Z style, a bit playful)
A call to action encouraging people to buy or pre-order
Optional emojis for Instagram/TikTok
Make 3 different versions:
Short caption (1–2 lines)
Medium caption (3–4 lines)
Promotional post with a strong selling tone
Keep it catchy, aesthetic, and scroll-stopping

